Hi!
It's possible I'm wrong. But for me it looks like:
n_sample <- 3000000
v <- round(runif(n_sample, 0, 100), 2)
m <- matrix(v, ncol = 10)
m_s <- t(apply(m, 1, sort))
m_d <- t(apply(m_s, 1, diff))
m_5 <- m_d>=5
f <- rowSums(m_5) == 9
sum(f)
res <- m_s[f, ]
Regards,
Sergiy

