As a workaround, you could do something like this:

   raw <- readChar("test.txt", 1000)
   raw <- gsub("\r\n", "\n", raw)
   raw <- gsub("\r", "\n", raw)
   strsplit(raw, "\n")[[1]]
   ## [1] "Line 1" ""       "Line 3"


Of course, if the true file was created with

   txt <- paste0("Line 1\r", "\n", "\r\n", "Line 4\r")

then "Line 1\r" and "\n"  will be merged into one line.



